OL,6,FThe party has called for the Scottish
OL,7,Fgovernment to ensure any obstacles in
OL,8,Fbringing instances of upskirting to
OL,9,Fcourt are resolved to ensure offenders
OL,10,Fcan be prosecuted.
OL,12,FUpskirting involves a person taking
OL,13,Fimages or videos underneath someone's
OL,14,Fclothing without permission.
OL,16,FThe Lib Dems said "loopholes" in the
OL,17,Flaw mean offences only cover images
OL,18,Fobtained for motives of sexual
OL,19,Fgratification or for causing distress.
