OL,6,FLiam McArthur, the party's justice
OL,7,Fspokesman at Holyrood, urged the
OL,8,Fgovernment to review the law around
OL,9,Fupskirting.
OL,11,FHe said: "I would love to think that
OL,12,Fthese limited number of offences
OL,13,Frepresented the sum total of
OL,14,Fupskirting offences in our country.
OL,16,F"However, the reality is that victims
OL,17,Falready feel a sense of shame when
OL,18,Freporting offenders to the police and
OL,19,Fworry that there will be no
OL,20,Fconsequences.
